==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unkennel
<hw>Un*ken"nel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>kennel</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To drive from a kennel or hole; <as>as, to
<ex>unkennel</ex> a fox</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fig.: To discover; to disclose.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unkent</ent>⟦br⟧
